Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:02.78,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:09.80,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,That octopus currently thinks our \Ndomains are pushing for control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.04,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,But my goal is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.99,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open a small hole
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.05,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,in the barrier of this domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.30,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,The hole I entered through \Nis already sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:24.41,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,It's harder to open one \Nfrom inside than outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:29.07,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,but I can open a hole large enough for \Nsomeone to pass through for a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.14,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,The edge of his domain is beneath my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:33.57,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell, since I touched it when I entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:34.86,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready to go at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.97,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,If all three of you jump in at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:41.42,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,None of this leaving yourself \Nbehind alone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.82,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm risking my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.74,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't intend to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:49.74,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 39\N{\fs30\fscy150}Fluctuations, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:55.74,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.25,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:05.63,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They faced an enemy \Nthat understood language.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:11.18,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And with faith in their fellow grade-1 \Nindirectly conveying his intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:14.98,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the previously excluded possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:20.00,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,of escaping the domain became \Nan option once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.21,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,They're bolstering their defense of the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:26.94,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,That just groups them up for me to—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:27.95,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:30.56,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He figured it out?! But it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.82,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,To Fushiguro-kun's feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:51.76,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,One who had inherited the curse \Nof the Zen'in clan from birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:57.85,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and one who could not \Ncompletely cast off that curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:00.63,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,both stood in witness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.86,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,to the one who cast it all off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.86,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,now manifested in raw flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.36,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:14.86,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.30,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.37,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,A sorcerer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:24.38,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,They brought a new sorcerer \Nin instead of escaping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:32.39,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast! He was just in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.76,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.02,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,What's with his strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.22,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:45.44,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't feel any cursed energy from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.44,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,Did I just lose a contest of pure strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.74,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,Me, of all people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.23,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.36,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:54.14,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,The hole has been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.75,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,To make things worse, \Nit just figured out our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.24,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,It won't let us open a hole as easily again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.20,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,Toji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:18.01,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Ogami's seance technique \Nstill continued after her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.66,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Her summoning of the dead \Nshould have ceased
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:24.70,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,once her grandson, the vessel, \Nran out of cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:30.60,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But there was no cursed energy \Nin the grandson's soul
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.81,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,that was overwritten by Toji Zen'in's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:36.70,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and his body never expended \Ncursed energy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:41.02,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Her technique had lost \Nits chance to terminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:46.44,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The compounding irregularities \Nleft her technique running rampant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.66,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and Toji Zen'in was currently \Nfighting as directed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.96,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,by his instincts until his \Nvessel ultimately broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.08,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,He had become a murder machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.72,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:00.88,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,has no cursed energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.39,Main,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,Not worth my attention, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.00,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His fangs were constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:31.00,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,directed toward the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:46.06,Show_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,825)\pos(320,10)\3c&H8ECEDD&}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs16\bord0\fscy100\c&HDEDCE0&}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.24,Main,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,Old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.19,Main,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.10,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.63,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro-kun, can you \Nhold out a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.06,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.10,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.22,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We're placing our bets on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.48,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,He's smashing Playful Cloud against itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.73,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He's changing its shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:10.96,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Is he sharpening it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.80,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:28.06,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,Against a human with no cursed energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.76,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.64,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel that young \Nboy's domain weakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:36.27,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,If I can regain my guaranteed-hit \Neffect, I can kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:37.76,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.52,Italics,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,buy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.82,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you can hover, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.52,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need to say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.66,Main,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.34,Main,Dagon,0000,0000,0000,,over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.98,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,The domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.98,Italics,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,He seriously exorcised \Nthat octopus all by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:37.78,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If Fushiguro-kun hadn't come,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.27,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,we all would've been wiped out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.86,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Though problems still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.07,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an ally or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.00,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.32,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,When did I get forced outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.59,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,This goes beyond just fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.59,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,He might be worse than Sukuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:41.12,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.55,Main,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.92,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,You've passed on, Dagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.51,Italics,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.87,Italics,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.62,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This one's another level stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.82,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.62,Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,...than that cursed spirit, Dagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:10.39,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Our souls will reincarnate, \Neven without relying on human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.42,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again in the \Nwasteland a century from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.14,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.39,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,First one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:29.64,Main,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,Nana—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.40,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Second one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.13,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Third one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.12,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Sukuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.68,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.80,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,The fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:13.06,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has released Sukuna's \Nfingers somewhere here in Shibuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.71,Main,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.91,Main,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,The fingers might draw cursed spirits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.57,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.28,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.18,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:28.30,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Sukuna-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.43,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,You two! How many fingers did you feed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.36,Main,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.43,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Mimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.44,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,That so? Then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.07,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Good, the markings haven't disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:02.58,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,This was an unexpected turn of events, \Nbut I'll make use of it to greatest effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:07.95,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Yuji Itadori probably wouldn't \Ntransfer control of his body to Sukuna
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.73,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,even after taking in all 20 fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:19.21,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only if he spent \N20 days taking one in every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.22,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,If he took in ten at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.40,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,his body wouldn't be able \Nto adapt quickly enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:28.80,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,and control would transfer to Sukuna, \Neven if only temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.98,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.55,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Sukuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.99,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H213835&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.99,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\3c&HA0DCE8&\pos(320,18)\c&H292619&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.99,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H213835&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.99,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\3c&HA0DCE8&\pos(320,18)\c&H354F3E&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.88,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I fed him all ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:16.22,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Now there should be at least \N15 fingers inside Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:28.32,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.32,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Must have been the technique of one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:35.46,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,But given how frightened they are, \NI doubt they can stop me that many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.68,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.10,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.59,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.61,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sukuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.60,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Strength of a different kind than Satoru Gojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.10,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Overwhelming evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:09.62,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Fear that even the slightest \Nmove could lead to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.07,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.12,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe, breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.22,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe, breathe, breathe, breathe, breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.02,Italics,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to breathe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.10,Italics,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,He won't kill us for that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.14,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You hold your heads quite high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.16,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Did you believe taking one knee was enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.15,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest men bow \Nthe lowest, or so it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.79,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I see you value your head quite lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:03.68,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You brats,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.93,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.17,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You wished to speak to me, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.32,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll grant you a finger's worth of audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.68,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Now speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:26.42,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,B-Below us, there's a man in monk's robes \Nwith a suture across his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:34.16,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:41.34,Main,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,Please free Geto-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.84,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Geto-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.50,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Satoru Gojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.50,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,He's super strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.48,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.91,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,He was my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.44,Flashback,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,But we had a fight and haven't spoken since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.80,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.38,Flashback,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:13.86,Flashback,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.00,Flashback,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:26.38,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never forgive Satoru Gojo for \Nkilling Geto-sama, so long as we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.88,Italics,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,But we did feel that was appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.60,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:35.64,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo was Geto-sama's \None and only best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.64,Italics,Mimiko,0000,0000,0000,,But you are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.21,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.73,Italics,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make you regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.84,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,We know the location of one other finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.66,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll kill that man for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:55.36,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,we'll tell you where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.46,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:00.12,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.77,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Mimiko! Mimiko! Mimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.12,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think a measly one or two fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.12,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mimiko! Mimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.72,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,would grant you the right to order me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.73,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No! Mimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:27.56,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.35,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Mimiko! Mimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.74,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,How offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.23,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:33.69,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Sukuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.40,Main,Nanako,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.26,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.30,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,No, the photo function, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:20:00.05,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably some ability to do something \Nto whatever was pictured in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:01.60,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.31,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're next, cursed spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.79,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.20,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.30,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.24,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:22.51,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Our objective, Sukuna, \Nis your complete resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:28.88,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, you only have temporary freedom \Nwhile Itadori struggles to adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:32.88,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're the most \Naware of that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:39.58,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Sukuna's Reverse Cursed Technique \Nis capable of healing others as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:41.70,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,it can't do anything about the shape of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.26,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,a soul once it's changed by \NMahito's Idle Transfiguration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:51.78,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that he didn't forge a pact back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.84,Italics,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,It was that he couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:21:00.58,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Forge a pact with Yuji Itadori \Nbefore he returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:05.33,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,A pact to grant you perpetual \Nauthority over his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:10.14,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Many of Itadori's allies are already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.18,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of ways you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.75,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.40,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I already have my own plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.80,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,But I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:33.37,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,You all are desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:37.69,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,This is your reward for the fingers. Come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.94,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,If you manage to land even \Na single blow on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:44.20,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work under you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:53.20,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, how about \NI slaughter every human in Shibuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.77,Main,Sukuna,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:07.12,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,You're true to your word, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:44.48,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to use jujutsu, \Nyou should do it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:44.47,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um, there are minors present.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:47.07,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier! Technique! One, two, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:47.52,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please, students are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.03,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,I threw out paper, so all \Nof you who threw scissors
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.07,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,might see something \Ngood happening tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:52.35,Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please don't suddenly try \Nto make this kid-friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.99,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Thunderclap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:53.45,Main,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next time, "Thunderclap."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:54.86,Main,Naobito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm so drunk!

